    "data": [
        {
            "title": "工行半年歸母淨利潤按年降1.4% 計提資產減值損失1045.29億元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">工商銀行(01398)公布，上半年歸屬母公司股東淨利潤1681.03億元(人民幣．下同)，按年減少1.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/bplib_20230705-125857_source-web_中國工商銀行01398-年報相片_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/bplib_20230705-125857_source-web_中國工商銀行01398-年報相片_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">期內實現營業收入4090.82億元，較去年同期提升1.8%。其中利息淨收入3135.76億元，按年微降0.1%；非利息收入955.06億元，增長8.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">受貸款市場報價利率(LPR)下調、存量房貸利率調整、存款期限結構變動等因素影響，年化淨利息差和淨利息收益率分別為1.16%和1.3%，按年分別下降0.08個百分點和0.13個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">計提資產減值損失1045.29億元，增長2.4%。計提信用減值損失1040.07億元，按年增2.2%；其中貸款減值損失1022.15億元，增加8.1%；其他資產減值損失5.22億元，增加1.01倍。半年實現淨利潤1688.03億元，按年跌1.5%，年化平均總資產回報率0.67%，年化加權平均權益回報率8.82%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"工商銀行官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01398-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"工商銀行官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/01398-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">工商銀行官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">截至6月底時，不良貸款率1.33%，較去年底減少0.01個百分點。拯備覆蓋率217.71%，較去年底提升2.8個百分點。貸款撥備率2.89%，較去年底增0.02個百分點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">核心一級資本充足率13.89%，較去年底的14.1%減少0.21個百分點；一級資本率足率由去年底的15.36%升至今年6月底的15.25%。資本充足率由去年底的19.39%升至今年6月底時19.54%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215828-%e5%b7%a5%e8%a1%8c%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e6%ad%b8%e6%af%8d%e6%b7%a8%e5%88%a9%e6%bd%a4%e6%8c%89%e5%b9%b4%e9%99%8d1-4-%e8%a8%88%e6%8f%90%e8%b3%87%e7%94%a2%e6%b8%9b%e5%80%bc%e6%90%8d%e5%a4%b11045-29%e5%84%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20230719_FI_source_licensed_01398_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-29 17:00:33",
