        {
            "title": "全日收市｜港股收升78點  生科股上揚  全周計科指累跌近1.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股收市升幅收窄至78點，生科股今造好，電沲升幅略收窄，一周計恒指趺226點，科指累近1.5%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">港股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數全日收報25077點，升78點或0.32%，甫開市即收復二萬五關口，報25095點，升96點或0.39%，最低見25066，升68點或0.27%，隨即反覆向上，最高見25277，升279點或1.12%，為全日高位，午後波不超過上午。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"港股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"港股 AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">港股 AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數全日報5674，升30點或0.54%，今早開報5689點，升45點或0.8%；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生國企指數全日報8947，升30點或0.35%，今早以8958點開市，升41點或0.46%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指一周累跌226點或0.89%，科指一周累升27點或0.48%，國指累跌132點或1.45%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">9月期指升117點或0.47%，報25023，低水55點 ; 科指期貨升43點或0.76%，報5694點，高水20點 ; 國指期貨報8930，升43點或0.48%，低水18點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交3356.01億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241119_FI_source-web_00285-3-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：比亞迪電子官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪電子(00285)升7.3%，報41.18元，為表現最佳藍籌股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">生科醫藥股造好，石藥(01093)升6.67%，報10.07元 ; 藥明康德(02359)升6.52%，報107.9元 ; 藥明生物(02269)升6.96%，報33.2元 ;中生製藥(01177)揚5.46%，報8.17元。       </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">信達生物(01801)升6.84%，報96.85元 ; 剛公布配股的科笛(02487)飆20.94%，報11.55元 ; 和鉑醫藥(02142)飛升15.91%，報14.72元 ; 微創機器人(02252)升4.42%，報20.32元，中期虧損收窄至1.13億元人民幣。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：石藥集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/20241115_FI_source-web_01093.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：石藥集團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">電池股升，寧德時代(03750)升4.18%，報424.2元 ; 贛鋒鋰業(01772)升4.26%，報31/36元 ; 天齊鋰業(09696)升1.85%，報40.66元 ; 瑞浦蘭鈞(00666)升6.2%，報11.99元 ; 中創新航(03931)升5.88%，報22.7元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">蒙牛乳業(02319)全日領跌，收跌4.04%，報15.2元，為表現最差藍籌股。東方海外(00316)收跌3.47%，報136.3元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國泰君安國際(01788)宣布推全新加密貨幣交易服務，今早股價狂飆，曾升23.14%，報5.88元，全日收升15.69%，報5.9元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/20230719_FI_source-web_蒙牛乳業02319-2.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：蒙牛乳業官網</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15215827-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%bd%9c%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%8778%e9%bb%9e-%e7%94%9f%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%8a%e6%8f%9a-%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e8%a8%88%e7%a7%91%e6%8c%87%e7%b4%af",
